>> B2: Describe your code for traversing a user-specified path.  How
>> do traversals of absolute and relative paths differ?

I was not able to successfully implement subdirectories. After parsing the
file paths, if the first char is a "/" I would start the traversal
at the root directory. Else, I would set the start of the traversal at the
current working directory. 

